results.title: Poster: Love, Laugh, Live, Saying, Picture, Mural, Photo, Frame, Decoration, Living Room, Bedroom, Typography
results.description:
Poster with saying: Love, Laugh, Live

Our posters are all produced on high-quality Fuji paper weighing 230g/m2. The surface has a matte finish so that the poster does not later reflect on the wall and even dark areas are always clearly recognizable.

Our poster sizes are designed to frame the posters with a passepartout. For this reason, the posters are slightly larger than the specified DIN formats. The exact size of the A4 format poster is 21 x 30 cm and the size of the A3 poster is 30 x 45 cm. This way, they can be easily hung behind a passepartout with the corresponding DIN formats.
